1151
00:42:08,186 --> 00:42:09,586
This thing blew up to this extent.

1152
00:42:09,626 --> 00:42:10,427
Why didn't you

1153
00:42:10,427 --> 00:42:11,466
call me and tell me?

1154
00:42:11,947 --> 00:42:13,546
Why should I call you?

1155
00:42:13,666 --> 00:42:14,867
Would telling you do any good?

1156
00:42:15,666 --> 00:42:16,267
If it did,

1157
00:42:16,307 --> 00:42:17,626
would the drama have lasted so long?

1158
00:42:19,827 --> 00:42:20,427
Okay.

1159
00:42:22,787 --> 00:42:23,787
What about this?

1160
00:42:24,427 --> 00:42:25,267
Why don't you...

1161
00:42:25,666 --> 00:42:27,106
