1173
00:42:49,026 --> 00:42:50,307
Who does she think can last longer?

1174
00:42:52,626 --> 00:42:53,707
Must you drag this out?

1175
00:42:53,986 --> 00:42:54,867
I'm not the one dragging this out.

1176
00:42:55,267 --> 00:42:56,106
It's because your mom

1177
